00043 bool hasLowerMass(const AminoAcid::Info::Record& a, const AminoAcid::Info::Record& b)
00044 {
00045     return a.formula.monoisotopicMass() < b.formula.monoisotopicMass();
00046 }

00049 void printRecord(ostream* os, const AminoAcid::Info::Record& record)
00050 {
00051     if (!os) return;
00052 
00053         Chemistry::Formula water_("H2O1");
00054         Chemistry::Formula residueFormula = record.formula - water_;
00055     
00056     *os << record.symbol << ": " 
00057         << setw(14) << record.name << " " 
00058         << setw(11) << record.formula << " " 
00059         << setprecision(3)
00060         << setw(5) << record.abundance << " "
00061         << fixed 
00062         << setw(7) << record.formula.monoisotopicMass() << " "
00063         << setw(7) << residueFormula.monoisotopicMass() << endl;
00064 }

00067 void test()

00070 
00071     unit_assert(info[Alanine].formula[C] == 3);

00079 void printAminoAcidInfo()
00080 {
00081     AminoAcid::Info info;
00082         Chemistry::Formula water_("H2O1");
00083 
00084     // get a copy of all the records
00085 
00086     vector<AminoAcid::Info::Record> records;
00087 
00088     for (char symbol='A'; symbol<='Z'; symbol++)
00089     {
00090         try 
00091         {
00092             const AminoAcid::Info::Record& record = info[symbol];
00093             records.push_back(record);
00094         }
00095         catch (exception&)
00096         {}
00097     }
00098 
00099     // compute some averages
00100 
00101     double averageMonoisotopicMass = 0;
00102     double averageC = 0;
00103     double averageH = 0;
00104     double averageN = 0;
00105     double averageO = 0;
00106     double averageS = 0;
00107 
00108     for (vector<AminoAcid::Info::Record>::iterator it=records.begin(); it!=records.end(); ++it)
00109     {
00110         const AminoAcid::Info::Record& record = *it;
00111         printRecord(os_, record);
00112 
00113         Chemistry::Formula residueFormula = record.formula - water_;
00114         averageMonoisotopicMass += record.formula.monoisotopicMass() * record.abundance; 
00115         averageC += residueFormula[C] * record.abundance;
00116         averageH += residueFormula[H] * record.abundance;
00117         averageN += residueFormula[N] * record.abundance;
00118         averageO += residueFormula[O] * record.abundance;
00119         averageS += residueFormula[S] * record.abundance;
00120     }
00121 
00122     if (os_) *os_ << setprecision(8) << endl;
00123     if (os_) *os_ << "average residue C: " << averageC << endl;    
00124     if (os_) *os_ << "average residue H: " << averageH << endl;    
00125     if (os_) *os_ << "average residue N: " << averageN << endl;    
00126     if (os_) *os_ << "average residue O: " << averageO << endl;    
00127     if (os_) *os_ << "average residue S: " << averageS << endl;    
00128     if (os_) *os_ << endl;
00129 
00130     if (os_) *os_ << "average monoisotopic mass: " << averageMonoisotopicMass << endl;
00131     double averageResidueMass = averageMonoisotopicMass - water_.monoisotopicMass();
00132     if (os_) *os_ << "average residue mass: " << averageResidueMass << endl << endl;
00133 
00134     // sort by monoisotopic mass and print again
00135     sort(records.begin(), records.end(), hasLowerMass);
00136     for (vector<AminoAcid::Info::Record>::iterator it=records.begin(); it!=records.end(); ++it)
00137         printRecord(os_, *it); 
00138 }
